      "review_summary": "The branch updates Windsurf auto session import to read complete app.devin.ai and legacy windsurf.com localStorage bundles separately, keeps raw LevelDB text scan as a final fallback candidate, and adds docs plus focused tests.\n\nReproducibility: Source-reproducible: current main reads structured Windsurf Devin session keys only from windsurf.com before a raw text scan, while the linked report says the flow moved through app.devin.ai and Windsurf usage fetches fail. I did not run live browser-cookie probes because repository policy says not to do that unless explicitly requested.",
